From 61fadf5dcb4f4bf9fec276daf82c1d2ad64c010e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2026 10:03:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add Consent Records module: audit ledger, filters, export
 and detail drawer

Adds GET /api/dashboard/consent-records (paginated/filterable/sortable
ledger + summary metrics), /:id (record detail with purpose selection,
widget version, source/method) and /export (CSV, Excel, PDF with
filtered/selected/all/date-range scopes), backed entirely by
consent_events. Adds the Consent Records portal page with summary
cards, filters, sortable table, pagination, export menu and detail
drawer, wired into the portal nav.
